+
+  /* ============================================================
+     USE CASES PIN-SCROLL  (3.0 round 13)
+     The section is 600vh tall; the sticky child pins at top:64px so
+     vertical scroll across the section's range converts to horizontal
+     card advance. When the section is fully inside the viewport the
