+│  ▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓ │
+│                                         │
+│   Backtest win rates                    │  ← 22px / 600, 18px LR
+│   Stop guessing who's good. See         │  ← 16px body
+│   exactly which calls made money...     │
+│   ┌───────────────────────────────┐    │
+│   │  Open playbook ↗              │    │  ← 44h, 14px font
+│   └───────────────────────────────┘    │
